Jason wrote:

>>and I would like some advice
on the easiest way to reach the master cylinder/switch on the Bus.<<

Jason,

crawl under the bus just behind the driver's seat & look straight up - 
you'll see the master cylinder & booster right above you.

check the grounds & tail light assemblies first. then, you might
be able to check the switches with a VOM without removing them.

good luck,

